    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of September 17 article on wedding of Sarah Montague Mason and Terrence Michael Burgess, which misstated couple's married name, which is Burgess and misstated bridegroom's mother's name, Nancy Burgess (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report last Sunday about the wedding of Sarah Montague Mason and Terrence Michael Burgess misstated the couple's married name. They are Mr. and Mrs. Burgess, not Mason. The report also misstated the surname of the bridegroom's mother at one point. As noted elsewhere, she is Nancy Burgess, not Mason.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
